: "9167", "name": "Anthony Sophos", "qid": null, "roles": ["cello"]}, {"id": "9926", "name": "Sy Berger", "qid": null, "roles": ["trombone"]}, {"id": "11955", "name": "Paul Faulise", "qid": "Q26250511", "roles": ["bass_trombone"]}, {"id": "22843", "name": "Romeo Penque", "qid": "Q111734787", "roles": ["flute", "tenor_saxophone"]}, {"id": "23133", "name": "Alfred Brown", "qid": null, "roles": ["violin"]}, {"id": "25261", "name": "Al Cohn", "qid": "Q1382232", "roles": ["tenor_saxophone"]}, {"id": "26706", "name": "Jack Lesberg", "qid": "Q1677101", "roles": ["double_bass"]}, {"id": "31179", "name": "Joe Soldo", "qid": null, "roles": ["alto_saxophone", "flute"]}, {"id": "40728", "name": "Billy Exiner", "qid": null, "roles": ["drums"]}, {"id": "41189", "name": "Ralph Sharon", "qid": "Q611577", "roles": ["piano"]}, {"id": "44412", "name": "Frank Rehak", "qid": "Q1444006", "roles": ["trombone"]}, {"id": "44577", "name": "Cándido Camero", "qid": "Q83693", "roles": ["bongo_drums", "congas"]}, {"id": "50443", "name": "Eddie Costa", "qid": "Q489518", "roles": ["vibraphone"]}, {"id": "51379", "name": "Dick Meldonian", "qid": "Q1209734", "roles": ["alto_saxophone", "flute"]}, {"id": "51689", "name": "Mel Davis", "qid": "Q6810684", "roles": ["trumpet"]}, {"id": "52517", "name": "Kenny Burrell", "qid": "Q255355", "roles": ["guitar"]}, {"id": "54662", "name": "Bobby Rosengarden", "qid": "Q470277", "roles": ["percussion", "timpani"]}, {"id": "56299", "name": "Berl Snyder", "qid": null, "roles": ["violin"]}, {"id": "56300", "name": "Joe Malinaggi", "qid": null, "roles": ["violin"]}, {"id": "60322", "name": "Bernie Glow", "qid": "Q826556", "roles": ["trumpet"]}, {"id": "61209", "name": "Al De Risi", "qid": null, "roles": ["trumpet"]}]}], "quotes": [{"speaker": "Candido Camero", "qid": "Q83693", "text": "Well, I went to work with Tony Bennett at the time. I went to work with Tony Bennett and also we toured the entire United States. Then we went to South America, Canada and Venezuela and I recorded with him a number of times too - a huge concert at Carnegie Hall that was recorded. And now in the book on his life which is entitled, Better Life, he mentions my name several times and speaks highly of me and aside from that, he has also included some pictures of me in the book where I appear working with him. That was the first recording I did with him that is called The Beat of My Heart by Tony Bennett.", "caption": "Candido recalls recording with Tony Bennett at Carnegie Hall", "conf": "high", "first_person": true, "doc_title": "Candido Camero — Smithsonian Jazz Oral History", "collection": "si", "url": "https://amhistory.si.edu/jazz/Camero-Candido/Camero_Candido_Transcript.pdf"}], "featured_people": [{"qid": "Q1382232", "id": "25261", "name": "Al Cohn"}, {"qid": "Q826556", "id": "60322", "name": "Bernie Glow"}, {"qid": "Q470277", "id": "54662", "name": "Bobby Rosengarden"}, {"qid": "Q83693", "id": "44577", "name": "Cándido Camero"}, {"qid": "Q1209734", "id": "51379", "name": "Dick Meldonian"}, {"qid": "Q489518", "id": "50443", "name": "Eddie Costa"}, {"qid": "Q1444006", "id": "44412", "name": "Frank Rehak"}, {"qid": "Q1677101", "id": "26706", "name": "Jack Lesberg"}, {"qid": "Q255355", "id": "52517", "name": "Kenny Burrell"}, {"qid": "Q6810684", "id": "51689", "name": "Mel Davis"}, {"qid": "Q1985553", "id": "7177", "name": "Nick Travis"}, {"qid": "Q26250511", "id": "11955", "name": "Paul Faulise"}, {"qid": "Q611577", "id": "41189", "name": "Ralph Sharon"}, {"qid": "Q111734787", "id": "22843", "name": "Romeo Penque"}, {"qid": "Q296729", "id": "59936", "name": "Tony Bennett"}]}